cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CR 

The paper deals with the impact of image modifications on content-based image retrieval (CBIR), which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also discusses the use of neural networks (cs.LG) and the challenges faced by multimedia researchers in studying adversarial queries (cs.CR). Finally, the paper presents an experimental analysis of CBIR, which falls under information retrieval (cs.IR).
